sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant Ctrl as InventoryController
    participant Svc as InventoryService
    participant Repo as InventoryRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Note over C,DB: GET /api/inventory/transactions?PageIndex=1&PageSize=20&...

    C->>+Ctrl: GET /transactions (GetTransactionsFilterRequest)
    Ctrl->>+Svc: GetTransactionsAsync(filter, ct)
    Svc->>+Repo: GetTransactionsPagedAsync(filter, ct)

    Repo->>+DB: SELECT InventoryTransactions JOIN TypeLv, StatusLv, ExportReasonLv, Supplier, CreatedBy, ApprovedBy, Items with filters (Search, TypeLvId, StatusLvId, ExportReasonLvId, SupplierId, FromDate, ToDate) ORDER BY CreatedAt DESC
    DB-->>-Repo: Rows
    Note right of Repo: Map to InventoryTransactionListDto with ItemCount and TotalValue
    Repo-->>-Svc: PagedResultDTO of InventoryTransactionListDto
    Svc-->>-Ctrl: PagedResultDTO of InventoryTransactionListDto
    Ctrl-->>-C: 200 ApiResponse with PagedResultDTO of InventoryTransactionListDto

    Note over C,DB: GET /api/inventory/transactions/{id}

    C->>+Ctrl: GET /transactions/{id}
    Ctrl->>+Svc: GetTransactionDetailAsync(id, ct)
    Svc->>+Repo: GetTransactionByIdAsync(id, ct)

    Repo->>+DB: SELECT InventoryTransaction with Includes (TypeLv, StatusLv, ExportReasonLv, Supplier, CreatedBy, ApprovedBy, Items->Ingredient->Image, Items->Ingredient->CategoryLv, Items->UnitLv, Items->VarianceReasonLv, Media->MediaAsset)
    DB-->>-Repo: InventoryTransaction entity

    alt entity is null
        Repo-->>Svc: null
        Svc-->>C: KeyNotFoundException
    end

    Repo-->>-Svc: InventoryTransaction entity
    Svc->>Svc: MapToDetailDto(entity)
    Svc-->>-Ctrl: InventoryTransactionDetailDto
    Ctrl-->>-C: 200 ApiResponse with InventoryTransactionDetailDto